/**
 * German-first quiz banks for Cybersicherheit SoSe 2025.
 *
 * One QuizSet per lesson (id `cs-2025-l<N>`, referenced by `Lecture.quizBankId`).
 * Each set holds MANY quizzes built from the themed menu in AGENTS.md
 * (Quiz bank — the system): one or two complete runs that cover the whole
 * chapter single-handed, plus angle-quizzes (Begriffe, Konzepte, Szenario,
 * Rechnen, Wahr/Falsch, Fallen, Reverse, Gemischt) so re-takes never feel
 * like reciting a memorized run. Every question is grounded in the chapter's
 * lecture MD + its matched Übung + the chapter explanation, and carries a
 * short `explanation`. German is canonical; translation is the final pass.
 */

